Salon Riyora – Beauty Salon Booking Web Application

Project Overview
Salon Riyora is an interactive beauty salon booking web application that allows users to explore services, create accounts, log in, and book appointments online. The website features a responsive design and user-friendly interface.

Features
- Display salon services using card layouts
- User registration and login system
- Online appointment booking form
- JavaScript form validation
- Image slider on the home page
- Booking confirmation popup
- Smooth navigation and UI effects

Website Pages
- **Home Page** – Introduction, image slider, featured services  
- **Services Page** – List of salon services with images  
- **Booking Page** – Appointment booking form  
- **Contact Page** – Contact details and contact form  
- **Login Page** – User login  
- **Register Page** – User registration  

Technologies Used
- HTML  
- CSS  
- Bootstrap  
- JavaScript  

Purpose
This project demonstrates the development of a responsive and interactive salon booking website with basic user authentication using front-end web technologies.
